hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: The absence of gravity in space modifies human structures from bones to muscle and on down to cell morphology.
There is an increased amount of radiation outside of the earth atmosphere. For humans, increases in radiation over time can lead to a spectrum of illnesses.
Light/Dark cycles and exposure to sunlight have profound effects on the human body because we have evolved to synchronize with the Earth’s rotation.
